  "title": "F&B Attendant / Captain #81438",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Hotel Accommodation</li><li>Position Title: <strong>F&B Attendant / Captain</strong></li><li>Working Location: City Hall</li><li>Working Hours: Shift Work (5-days Work Week)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic $1800 - $2,500</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Welcome and greet customers when they arrive at the outlet.</li><li>Learn the products and be familiar with all menu items.</li><li>Present the menu clearly and suggest suitable food and drink options to customers.</li><li>Take orders using the point-of-sale (POS) system and serve orders to tables accurately.</li><li>Clear and reset tables according to hygiene standards and requirements.</li><li>Keep the service station clean and well-organised.</li><li>Carry out other assigned duties related to restaurant service and cleanliness.</li><li>Follow health, safety, food handling, and hygiene standards.</li><li>Respond to guest feedback promptly and professionally.</li><li>Attend briefings, meetings, and training sessions as assigned.</li><li>Perform other duties as directed by management.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Provide good customer service with a positive and helpful attitude.</li><li>Work well under pressure in a fast-paced environment.</li><li>Work well with team members and cooperate as a team.</li><li>Pay attention to quality and maintain standards in a fast-paced setting.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81438 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
